{"tid":824401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地根本唔忿氣咋嘛","createTime":"2018-09-17T05:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T05:40:33.000Z","uid":27274,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"86c6a0cf3d591df18404d339bdb1b3e0f5255170","tid":824401,"uid":27274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"星期六日掛足8號到10號<br />\n去到星期一掛返3號 咁個風真係走咗啦喎<br />\n唔忿氣要死死氣地返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有呀 屌9啲的士佬果啲仲好笑<br />\n收多你少少錢（大咬另計）都唔得？<br />\n人地搵命博架 你返風更都有多啲錢啦<br />\n收返原價你地都唔返工啦 的士佬咪唔揸囉 睇吓你地到時點返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a586846f0178f4d726027a071c01897db1b6f4b7","tid":824401,"uid":27274,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:35:55.000Z","msg":"齋收負評無人駁到<br />\n開始良心譴責緊自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93c302526108e74db36d72abcc6f54d42cb6ab2","tid":824401,"uid":150348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"吹啊"}]}